text.tspan: Echo, Siri, Samsung TV, Nest, and Cortana exemplify a new era of pervasive listening.
With these technologies come new affordances, complexities and challenges.
This invite-only, one-day summit brings together the smartest people creating and
examining pervasive listening devices for an open conversation to address the most
complex questions from a human perspective.
fosters this conversation and establishes a framework for
leading technologists, designers, academics and policy makers as these technologies
become a part of everyday life.
Partial Witness, Co-Chairs: Kate Crawford & Kati London

perspective representing design, technology, policy, and academic research to
